description: Andrzej Duda, 48, contracts coronavirus as his country hits a daily record of new cases.
title: Covid-19: Poland President Duda tests positive for virus
title_page: Covid-19: Poland President Duda tests positive for virus - BBC News
maintext: "I didn't have and I don't have any symptoms, especially the serious ones like lack of taste or lack of smell, but the result of the test is absolutely clear," Mr Duda said in a video message posted on Twitter.
